# Manlifts Tender Announcement

### Contract Details
The Correctional Service of Canada (CSC) is soliciting bids for the procurement of three (3) manlifts. This tender is open to suppliers who hold a Supply Arrangement (SA) under the Request for Supply Arrangement (RFSA) E60HS-18LIFT/A.

### Tender Information

| **Category** | **Information** |
| --- | --- |
| **Notice Type** | Demande de propositions (Request for Proposal) |
| **Procurement Method** | Concurrentielle - Appel d'offres sélectif (Competitive - Selective tendering) |
| **Trade Agreements** | *Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement* |
|  | *Canada-UK Trade Continuity Agreement (Canada-UK TCA)* |
|  | *Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)* |
|  | *Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)* |
|  | *World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)* |
|  | *Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)* |
|  | *Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (CUFTA)* |
| **Regions of Opportunity** | *Canada* |
| **Regions of Delivery** | *Canada* |
| **Contracting Entity** | Servie Correctionnel du Canada |
|  | Correctional Service of Canada |

### Tender Details

There will be no debriefing on the results of the bid solicitation. Bidders may request a written, by telephone, or in-person debriefing within 15 working days from receipt of notification that their bid was unsuccessful.

The requested delivery date for the above-mentioned goods is November 30, 2022.

### Tender Dates and Times
The procurement period for this contract began on August 8, 2022, at 9:00 AM and will closes on September 2, 2022, at 2:00 PM.

### Solicitation Amendment
Solicitation Amendment 001 is issued to extend the closing date of the solicitation. The new closing date is September 2, 2022, at 2:00 PM.

### Contact Information

*   Name: Rachel Rivet
*   Email: [rachel.rivet@csc-scc.gc.ca](mailto:rachel.rivet@csc-scc.gc.ca)
*   Telephone: (343) 553-297
